roles:
*Master:*
• See the color of all the cards;
• Your goal is to give hints that relate as many words as possible of your team's color so that your agents can find them\.

*Agentes*:
• Don't see the color of the cards;
• Your objective is to find the words of your team's color following the hints from your respective master\.

colors:
What happens depending on the color of the card chosen:
**>🔴 *Your color:* keep guessing;
>
>⚪️ *White:* skip the turn immediately;
>
>🔷 *Opponent color:* skip the turn immediately, and brings the opposing team one card closer to victory;
>
>⚫️ *Black:* loses the game immediately, giving victory to the opposing team\.||
